10 1. A MOTOR VEHICLE RENTAL OR LEASING COMPANY;
11 OR
12 2. A HOLDER OF A SPECIAL REGISTRATION PLATE
13 ISSUED UNDER TITLE 13, SUBTITLE 9, PART III OF THIS ARTICLE.
