1 (4) A LANE DIRECTION CONTROL SIGNAL MONITORING SYSTEM
2 OPERATOR SHALL FILL OUT AND SIGN A DAILY SET–UP LOG FOR A LANE DIRECTION
3 CONTROL SIGNAL MONITORING SYSTEM THAT:
4 (I) STATES THE DATE AND TIME WHEN AND THE LOCATION
